<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about Flask-CORS)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/flask-cors.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2017 11:23:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Flask-CORS解决Ajax跨域请求问题</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/flask-corsjie-jue-ajaxkua-yu-qing-qiu-wen-ti/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;在本地开发网站的过程中，js访问后端服务会出现&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code bash"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_42b613c4caa94dd196a6fcdbd808d0a9-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;已拦截跨源请求：同源策略禁止读取位于 http://192.168.99.100:8080/signup/ 的远程资源。（原因：CORS 头缺少 &lt;span class="s1"&gt;'Access-Control-Allow-Origin'&lt;/span&gt;）。
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;这时可以通过Flask-CORS解决问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、安装。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="code bash"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_3217a0f02fdc43f28263fc38bd0f96ea-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip install flask-cors
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、使用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;table class="codetable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos"&gt;&lt;div class="linenodiv"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/flask-corsjie-jue-ajaxkua-yu-qing-qiu-wen-ti/#rest_code_0043df372b044bbc8baf1c8bc07fb5ac-1"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/flask-corsjie-jue-ajaxkua-yu-qing-qiu-wen-ti/#rest_code_0043df372b044bbc8baf1c8bc07fb5ac-2"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/flask-corsjie-jue-ajaxkua-yu-qing-qiu-wen-ti/#rest_code_0043df372b044bbc8baf1c8bc07fb5ac-3"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code python"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_0043df372b044bbc8baf1c8bc07fb5ac-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="kn"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nn"&gt;flask_cors&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;CORS&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_0043df372b044bbc8baf1c8bc07fb5ac-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;global_app&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Flask&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="vm"&gt;__name__&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_0043df372b044bbc8baf1c8bc07fb5ac-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;CORS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;global_app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Ajax</category><category>Flask-CORS</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/flask-corsjie-jue-ajaxkua-yu-qing-qiu-wen-ti/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Feb 2017 04:59:14 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>